Set the default chunk size to 32kb

- When using 4kb as chunk size you really need a *stable* network. The large amount of smaller packets can trigger potentially more TCP retransmission and TCP reconnects when using Wifi.
The downside of 32kb is an extra delay of ~1.3sec in contrast to a chunk size of 4kb.
